  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0e1f2a3b4c5d6, type: 3}
  m_Name: Vyanika_Lore
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::GV.UI.CharacterLoreData
  characterName: Vyanika
  tagline: Stop moving and you fall. Stop fighting and your people die.
  rarity: Epic
  role: Mobility / Evasive
  regionLabel: Kingdom
  regionName: Garuda Vana
  factionLabel: Faction
  factionName: Garudajas
  powerClass: Supreme Astra Powers
  terrainMastery: Dual Terrain Mastery
  tharaResonance: Normal Thara Resonance
  backstory: "Born in Garuda Vana - the sky-kingdom of the Garudajas, perched
    on floating peaks above perpetual storms. Life among the Garudajas means constant
    motion; their territory shifts with the winds, and only the fastest survive. Garuda
    Vana is dying - its ancient Vimana stabilizers are failing, and the kingdom
    needs resources the lowland realms refuse to share. Vyanika leads raids on Ratna
    Shila's outer vaults and Nandana's supply caravans. She knows Ishvaya
    has sworn to stop her. She knows Aaryaveer wants to annex Garuda Vana's flight
    technology. Roudra in Daitya Giri simply wants the Garudajas crushed."
  strengths: "Fastest pilot in the Akasa Raajyas; untouchable when she has space to
    move\nSupreme Astra combined with Dual Terrain Mastery - lethal in the right
    hands\nControls the tempo of any engagement; she decides when and where fights
    happen"
  weaknesses: "Normal Thara Resonance - she can't sustain long engagements\n
    Paper-thin offense despite Supreme Astra class; speed comes at the cost of firepower\n
    The survival of Garuda Vana rests on her shoulders - the pressure fractures
    her focus"
  rivals: "Ishvaya - Defends the vaults she raids\nRoudra - Wants Garuda
    Vana destroyed\nAaryaveer - Nandana wants her flight tech"
